multiple byte processing with full-word instructions.wa method is described which allows parallelprocessing of packed data items using only ordinary full-word computer instructions, even though the processingrequires operations whose execution is contingent upon the value of a datum.  it provides a useful techniquefor processing small data items such as alphanumeric characters.cacm august, lamport, l..kbyte processing, character processing, packed data.c.ca jb january ,   : pm